OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FTwo years after a landslide victory,
OL,7,FStarmer will leave Downing Street as
OL,8,Fthe second shortest-serving Labour
OL,9,Fprime minister in history
OL,11,FThe son of a toolmaker, the man behind
OL,12,FLabour's seismic comeback after 14
OL,13,Fyears of Tory rule, and now, less than
OL,14,Ftwo years later, a leader ousted by
OL,15,Fhis own party.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
