OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FThe beginning of Keir Starmer's
OL,7,Fdownfall came after a catastrophic set
OL,8,Fof election results for the Labour
OL,9,FParty in May, in which it lost more
OL,10,Fthan 1,400 council seats across
OL,11,FEngland, and had little success in
OL,12,FScotland and Wales.
OL,14,FThen, Andy Burnham found his way back
OL,15,Fto parliament through the Makerfield
OL,16,Fby-election, piling on even more
OL,17,Fpressure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
