OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FOn Monday, after a weekend of intense
OL,7,Fdiscussions with allies, he stood in
OL,8,Ffront of Downing Street and announced
OL,9,Fhis resignation.
OL,11,FITV News looks at the meteoric rise
OL,12,Fand fall of the UK's 58th prime
OL,13,Fminister.
OL,15,FHumble beginnings
OL,17,FStarmer has often told the story of
OL,18,Fhis humble beginnings, especially
OL,19,Fduring the 2024 election campaign
OL,20,Ftrail.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
