OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FGrowing up in the small town of Oxted
OL,7,Fin Surrey, his father worked as a
OL,8,Ftoolmaker in a factory, and his mother
OL,9,Fwas a nurse in the NHS.
OL,11,FHe was the first of his family to go
OL,12,Fto university, graduating from Leeds
OL,13,Fin 1985 with a first-class law degree.
OL,15,FStarmer qualified as a lawyer in 1987
OL,16,Fand began his career working as a
OL,17,Fbarrister, going on to specialise in
OL,18,Fhuman rights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
