OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FAlmost three decades later, he was
OL,7,Fmade director of public prosecutions,
OL,8,Fputting him at the top of the Crown
OL,9,FProsecution Service (CPS).
OL,11,FDuring his tenure at the CPS, he
OL,12,Foversaw the prosecution of Stephen
OL,13,FLawrence's murderers and gave evidence
OL,14,Fat the Leveson inquiry.
OL,16,FIt was for this work that he was
OL,17,Fknighted by the then-Prince Charles
OL,18,Fduring a ceremony at Buckingham Palace
OL,19,Fin 2014.
OL,21,FLeading the Labour landslide
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
