OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FIn 2015, Starmer made the switch to
OL,7,Fpolitics, being voted into parliament
OL,8,Ffor the first time at the age of 52.
OL,10,FElected with a promise to tackle
OL,11,Finjustice, he has represented Holborn
OL,12,Fand St Pancras as an MP ever since.
OL,14,FHe soon earned a spot in Jeremy
OL,15,FCorbyn's shadow cabinet, serving as
OL,16,Fshadow Brexit secretary from October
OL,17,F2016 until April 2020, when he
OL,18,Freplaced his former boss at the top of
OL,19,Fthe party.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
