OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FUnder his new leadership, Starmer made
OL,7,Fpledges to kickstart the economy, make
OL,8,FBritain "a clean energy superpower"
OL,9,Fand rejuvenate the NHS.
OL,11,FHowever, the last two years have been
OL,12,Ftainted by several setbacks and
OL,13,Fscandals that have plagued the prime
OL,14,Fminister and given him little time to
OL,15,Fcelebrate the wins.
OL,17,FA premiership defined by U-turns
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
