OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FThe left wing of his party frustrated
OL,7,FStarmer's attempts to enforce his
OL,8,Fpolicies, notably in cutting its
OL,9,Fwelfare bill, forcing him into one
OL,10,Freversal after another.
OL,12,FRestricting the winter fuel allowance,
OL,13,Fkeeping the two-child benefit cap, and
OL,14,Fthe introduction of mandatory digital
OL,15,FIDs were all policies the government
OL,16,Fhas made U-turns on.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
