OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FIn May 2025, Starmer announced
OL,7,Fimmigration reforms in a speech
OL,8,Fmemorable for his assertion that the
OL,9,FUK risked becoming an "island of
OL,10,Fstrangers".
OL,12,FThe phrase, which Starmer later said
OL,13,Fhe "regretted", drew criticism from
OL,14,Fmany who likened it to Enoch Powell's
OL,15,Finflammatory 'Rivers of Blood' speech.
OL,17,FThe prime minister did, however, see
OL,18,Fsome domestic wins.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
