OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FThe NHS England waiting list for
OL,7,Froutine hospital appointments fell to
OL,8,Fits lowest level in nearly four years
OL,9,Fat the end of March 2026, and more
OL,10,Fthan 65% of patients began treatment
OL,11,Fwithin 18 weeks of referral - the NHS
OL,12,Ftarget -the same month, the highest
OL,13,Fpercentage since 2021.
OL,15,FNet migration was also brought down by
OL,16,F69% for the year ending June 2025 and
OL,17,Fthousands of families benefited from
OL,18,Fthe scrapping of the two-child benefit
OL,19,Fcap.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
