OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FTime will tell how popular other
OL,7,Fpolicies, such as the introduction of
OL,8,Fthe Renter's Rights Act, the
OL,9,FEmployment Rights Act, and bringing
OL,10,Frail back into national control, will
OL,11,Fbe.
OL,13,FInternational relations
OL,15,FOn the international stage, Starmer
OL,16,Fwas seen as having met with more
OL,17,Fsuccess.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
