OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FHe made headway in repairing relations
OL,7,Fwith the EU, claiming: "This Labour
OL,8,Fgovernment will be defined by
OL,9,Frebuilding our relationship with
OL,10,FEurope."
OL,12,FStarmer also used his premiership to
OL,13,Fstrike "landmark" trade deals with
OL,14,Fcountries such as India, and, along
OL,15,Fwith French President Emmanuel Macron,
OL,16,Fled the so-called "coalition of the
OL,17,Fwilling" to commit to forming a
OL,18,Fpeacekeeping force in Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
