OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782202689
OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FHowever, his relationship with Donald
OL,7,FTrump was a little more complicated,
OL,8,Finitially cultivating a good
OL,9,Frelationship with the US president,
OL,10,Fbefore they fell out over the war in
OL,11,FIran.
OL,13,FOn a visit to the White House in
OL,14,FFebruary 2025, the pair were all
OL,15,Fsmiles as Starmer handed Trump an
OL,16,Finvitation for a second state visit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
