SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782202689
OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FAs the American president triggered
OL,7,Fsweeping tariffs on countries in April
OL,8,Fof the same year, the UK and US agreed
OL,9,Fa deal that would protect British cars
OL,10,Fand planes.
OL,12,FThe pair's relationship soured after
OL,13,Fthe US and Israel launched strikes on
OL,14,FIran in February 2026 and the US
OL,15,Fpresident took umbrage with Starmer's
OL,16,Fapparent lack of support.
OL,18,FAt the time, he said he was "not
OL,19,Fhappy" with the prime minister,
OL,20,Fdescribing him as "not Winston
OL,21,FChurchill".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
