OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FThe Mandelson problem
OL,8,FHowever, it was through his
OL,9,Fdetermination to strengthen the bonds
OL,10,Fwith the White House that Starmer's
OL,11,Fjudgment was brought into question.
OL,13,FHis appointment of Lord Peter
OL,14,FMandelson as UK Ambassador to the US
OL,15,Fin December 2024 raised eyebrows at
OL,16,Fthe time, but it was the peer's
OL,17,Finclusion in the so-called Epstein
OL,18,Ffiles, released earlier this year,
OL,19,Fthat intensified anger.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782202689
OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FNot only was the extent of Lord
OL,7,FMandelson's friendship with the late
OL,8,Fpaedophile Jeffrey Epstein revealed,
OL,9,Fbut so was the indication that he
OL,10,Fleaked market-sensitive information to
OL,11,Fhim while he was a government minister.
OL,13,FAfter Mandelson was sacked, Starmer
OL,14,Fsaid he was "sorry for having believed
OL,15,FMandelson's lies" and insisted that
OL,16,F"none of us knew the depth of the
OL,17,Fdarkness" of the peer's relationship
OL,18,Fwith the convicted sex offender when
OL,19,Fhe was picked for the role.
OL,21,FLocal elections
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
