OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FThe disastrous May election results
OL,7,Fwere the final nail in the coffin for
OL,8,FStarmer, whose party saw big losses to
OL,9,FReform UK, the Green Party and Plaid
OL,10,FCymru.
OL,12,FIn the following days, Starmer doubled
OL,13,Fdown on his position, pledging to go
OL,14,Ffurther on defence, energy and in
OL,15,Fforging closer ties with Europe.
OL,17,FHowever, as Labour MP Catherine West,
OL,18,Fwho led the original charge against
OL,19,Fthe leader, stated, it was "too little
OL,20,Ftoo late".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
