OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782202689
OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,FResignation
OL,8,FIn an emotional resignation speech on
OL,9,FMonday, Starmer defended his record
OL,10,Fand pledged to give his successor "my
OL,11,Ffull and unequivocal support, knowing
OL,12,Fthat they will inherit a Britain that
OL,13,Fis far stronger and fairer than the
OL,14,Fone I inherited two years ago".
OL,26,@rD@cOUvD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
