PN,31920
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782202689
OL,3,CFrom Red Wall revival to party revolt:
OL,4,CHow Keir Starmer's career unfolded
OL,6,F"Thank you. Thank you. Walking up this
OL,7,Fstreet two years ago was the proudest
OL,8,Fmoment of my life. A new Labour
OL,9,Fgovernment. The first in 14 years. A
OL,10,Fpage in our country's history turned
OL,11,Fafter years of disappointment and
OL,12,Fdespair," he said.
OL,14,F"The chance to change the lives of
OL,15,Fmillions of people for the better.
OL,16,FThat's what I came into politics for.
OL,17,FThe journey to that point was not
OL,18,Feasy."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G20/21
